  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>In the morning you'll have a breakfast buffet. Half board evening meals are three courses of traditional Italian cuisine, with choices, along with a salad bar. You'll choose your food options a day in advance for each meal.</p>
<p>If you want to dine <span>à</span> la carte, there's a restaurant with an outdoor terrace serving up stone baked pizzas as well as seafood platters (payable locally). The outdoor dining terrace is only available to guests dining à la carte and the hotel only serve bottled water (free tap water is not available).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
