  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms </strong>sleep two people and are traditionally decorated.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Rooms with Side Lake View</strong> sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed on a mezzanine level).</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Air-conditioning (mid Jun-mid Sep)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €10 per day, payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €1.30 per person per day is payable locally</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
